title: Title Trackers
description:
Is there a classic album you love that has no title track? You know, like U2’s Joshua Tree, Bruce Springsteen’s Greetings From Asbury Park. Or what about Tom Petty’s Full Moon Fever? Ever wonder what those songs might have sounded like if the artists had written them? Well, finally someone has. 

Learn more about The Title Trackers

Listen to Lost Title Tracks on YouTube

Tell us what’s making you smile! Send a voice memo to smile@wondery.com 

Our theme song is “Smile” by Ryan Innes
